OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FDisability work tests to be
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fscrapped in shake-up       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Disability fit-for-work tests will be  
OL,6, abolished under reforms billed as the  
OL,7, "biggest change to our welfare system  
OL,8, in a decade" in Chancellor Jeremy      
OL,9, Hunt's Budget.                         
OL,11,FMr Hunt said benefit claimants will be 
OL,12,Fable to seek work "without fear of     
OL,13,Flosing financial support".             
OL,15,FCurrently, disability benefits can be  
OL,16,Freduced or withdrawn when a claimant   
OL,17,Freturns to work.                       
OL,19,FThe plans are part of Mr Hunt's drive  
OL,20,Fto get more people back into work.     
